<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (yạ yswʿ yạ ạbn ạllh .. yạ wạhb ạlḥyạẗ
 nʿln ạ̹nk ṣạḥb ạlslṭạn .. fy qlwbnạ wfy kl mkạn
 ạ̹nt wḥdk syd ʿly̱ kl ạlkwn .. llạ̉bd yạ yswʿ mhmạ ykwn)2
 1- ạlkdẖb ktẖyr ḥwạlynạ .. wạlḍlmẗ tgẖmy ʿynynạ
 wạlʿạlm ṣwth byʿly̱ .. wʿạyz yrbṭ ạ̹ydynạ
 (mhmạ tyjy ạlḥrwb .. wymly̱ ạldnyạ ẓlạm
 ạlmlạyyn btwb .. wbtmlạ ḥyạthạ slạm)2
 2- ạlʿạlm klh ậlạm .. ʿạlm mlyạn ạ̉ṣnạm
 msẖtạq lklmẗ ḥq .. tʿly̱ fwq kl ạlklạm
 (ạ̹ʿln yạ yswʿ ʿn mjdk .. llqlb ạlly bysẖtạq lk
 wbkrh hạyyjy ạlywm .. fyh kl ạlqlwb tkẖḍʿ lk)2</lyrics>
<title>yạ yswʿ yạ ạbn ạllh</title>
</song>